2.5 - Deleting entries Deleting an entry is pretty easy, it just requires the entry&rsquo;s DN. There is one important thing to understand though, if the entry has children, the operation will fail.
Simple entry deletion We request a deletion by providing the entry&rsquo;s DN, as in the following example:
